{"tid":302262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗女與人類交配，會生雜種BB嗎？","createTime":"2017-06-29T09:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T17:31:45.000Z","uid":50275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f7b05d1fa5b8b560f11a38b882a3c864a936a5","tid":302262,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"答案可能大家都知道，幸好，是不會。那為什麼馬與驢可以生雜種騾子？要了解動物的生殖能力，先要了解生殖隔離（Reproductive Isolation）。<br />\n生殖隔離分交配前隔離及交配後隔離，交配前隔離是個很簡單的概念，即插唔入，插唔入有許多原因，可能是發情期不一，亦可能是生理構造不同，例如人與螞蟻是不可能繁殖的。"},{"pid":"b7f4bf44cc9bc43ad173436d78bfa93c7c50cbb0","tid":302262,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56fd153a1d6ade03d537cce94931e6cf263638ed","tid":302262,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"以為講緊習近平<br />\n我都係出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3fed80d6d5272b30ef6a39bdf3f2292029ee0d","tid":302262,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為講緊習近平<br />\n我都係出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70f10a5ed330a347619c591ca6df75549910996","tid":302262,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"聽講好似要外國走狗同猿人交配　先出到隻　大雜種ＢＢ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10528be1327651ee4cdebaa271b4b636c80bd4a","tid":302262,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"Chromosome 數目唔同"},{"pid":"bddc74d650815e8eed67558ee5683106617f4c75","tid":302262,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces